{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Today corporate law treatises no longer mention the duty of obedience.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F26357692861_ID0EAUAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F26357692861_ID0EAUAE_1}
