{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The ALI Principles of Corporate Governance, which in the 1980s sought to summarize and guide U.S. corporate law, identified only the obligation of the 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
corporation
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 to \u8220\'3fact within the boundaries set by law\u8221\'3f--a notion based on \u8220\'3fthe moral norm of the 
}
