{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 But the ALI Principles did not go further to specify a duty of obedience for corporate actors, instead assuming only vaguely that shareholders could enforce the corporate compliance obligation, presumably by an injunctive action.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
