{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
The movement to see the corporation as private contract--and thus to delink it from non-corporate legal norms--reached its zenith with the legal contractarians.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F29357692861_ID0ERVAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F29357692861_ID0ERVAE_1}
