30
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 And those who saw the corporation as a board-centric team production moved to bury any duty to comply with internal corporation norms. Professors Blair and Stout declared that, while an agent owes an obedience duty to her principal, directors in for-profit corporations \u8220\'3fare not required to follow shareholder mandates in any way.\u8221\'3f
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F31357692861_ID0EPWAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F31357692861_ID0EPWAE_1}
