{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0EVXAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0EVXAE_1}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
State indemnification statutes made clear that the corporation could indemnify corporate actors against personal liability for a range of illegal acts.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
