{\b1 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
*465
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 statutes invited charter amendments to exculpate directors from personal liability, except in Delaware for \u8220\'3facts or omissions ... which involve ... a knowing violation of law\u8221\'3f
}
