\par 
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri400 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li700 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri400 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li700 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb400 
[I]nstead of being eliminated or collapsed under the umbrella of the duty of care, the duty of obedience should be more clearly delineated as one of the three fiduciary duties to which the not-for-profit corporate board is held, thereby sending an important message to the sector that fidelity to the institutional mission is critical.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F65357692861_ID0EMOAG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F65357692861_ID0EMOAG_1}
