{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Not only does this imply application of the business judgment rule to non-profit decisions, but \u8220\'3fthe charitable corporation and the business corporation begin to look and act like each other, regardless of rhetoric and tax status.\u8221\'3f
}
