{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0ES2AG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0ES2AG_1}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Without the duty of obedience, the decision whether to implement a system of internal controls would be subject only to the duty of care--and thus fall fully within the board\rquote s informed discretion under the business judgment rule. Without obedience, the issuance of backdated stock options would involve the question of whether the corporation had gotten its money\rquote s worth--and thus be a matter entirely of value, 
}
{\b1 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
{\*\bkmkstart co_pp_sp_1500_473_1}{\*\bkmkend co_pp_sp_1500_473_1}
{\b1 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
