{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0E6QBG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0E6QBG_1}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
The duties of care and loyalty--given the assumed contexts in which each arises--lack the linguistic and narrative force of a \u8220\'3fduty of obedience.\u8221\'3f It is no wonder, for example, that the Delaware courts have had such a hard time explaining why directors should have a duty to monitor compliance with non-corporate legal norms. 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Allis-Chalmers
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 offered no explanation as to why directors were obligated to pay attention to \u8220\'3fred flags\u8221\'3f;
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
